

======================================================================

1) go to src directory, and run:
   make all

2) ./fltkmakelist 

3) Have a look at the newly created files into the directory bin.

4) You can then instlal and/or run floffice.

======================================================================

Needed Packages:
  FLTK 1.3
  g++ and gcc 
  
If you would like to have X11 lightweight games: 
  xsol
  xmajhongg
  xdemineur
  xboard
  
Fluid if you would like to join the dev ! Welcome!

